Network Segmentation:

The two readings for today were about Network Segmentation and what is Network Segmentation. According to CISCO there are four benefits of network segmentation; Improve operational performance by reducing traffic, Limit cyberattack damage, Protect vulnerable devices, Reduce the scope of compliance by designing a network in a way that achieves regular compliance. The main reasons are for performance and security reasons for network segmentation. The zero trust response is to basically not trust any one on the network and to by default establish a perimeter and assume that nobody is trustworthy. 
